 ('95', '106', 'en_us', 'Balance Transfer Credit Cards', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The following balance transfer credit card offers from our partners are designed to help people consolidate their credit card debt onto one card, thus saving money on interest charges. Some of the credit card offers below even feature a low introductory 0% APR interest rate on credit card balance transfers.</p>', NULL, NULL, '', NULL, 'balance-transfer', '12', '3175896', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:03:34', '2016-03-26 00:58:54', 'a6427833-49e8-4342-914b-47110d64c4e1'),
 ('96', '107', 'en_us', 'Cash Back Credit Cards', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The following cash back credit cards from our partners feature reward programs that offer cash back or rebate incentives. A Cash Back Credit Card rewards you for using them with cash back incentives and rebate programs. Credit cards with cash rebates and incentives usually require a good to excellent credit rating for approval.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '15', '3181639', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:03:48', '2016-03-29 01:41:26', '2795e183-05be-49ae-bb52-2fabf95c1b26'),
 ('97', '108', 'en_us', 'Excellent Credit', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The following Credit Cards are for People with Excellent Credit. Compare offers from our partners side by side and apply online for the card that is right for you. Apply for the Excellent Credit card of your choice by completing a secure online application.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '76', '', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:04:01', '2016-04-02 15:27:30', 'a350a358-66ba-4d70-baba-1582362ac32d'),
 ('98', '109', 'en_us', '0% APR Credit Cards', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The primary benefit of a 0% APR credit card is the introductory 0% APR interest rate. This rate is available anywhere from 6 to 18 months or more from when the credit card account is opened. Depending on the card offer, it will be applied to new purchases, balance transfers or both. Compare 0% credit cards from our partners and apply online.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '1477', '3181638', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:04:48', '2016-04-01 21:41:37', '90fe036f-798d-4f2d-b92e-b34b5568cc0b'),
 ('99', '110', 'en_us', 'Low Interest Credit Cards', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The following Low Interest Credit Cards from our partners feature either a low fixed rate APR or a low introductory APR. Apply for the credit card of your choice by filling out a secure online application.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '11', '3181635', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:05:01', '2016-03-29 01:30:47', 'e58bec35-bd0b-4334-9599-5b2480011b3c'),
 ('100', '111', 'en_us', 'No Annual Fee Credit Cards', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The following cards from our partners save you money by not charging an annual fee. Some of the cards listed below waive the annual fee for the first year, but may charge a fee for subsequent years. Some even offer rewards and low interest rates.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '2005', '', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:05:24', '2016-03-29 01:34:13', '2f0e6371-f3cb-4752-83e1-9261686ad8ea'),
 ('101', '112', 'en_us', 'No Foreign Transaction Fee Credit Cards', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The following cards save you money when you travel outside the United States by not charging a foreign transaction fee. These cards are attractive to cardholders who travel overseas, and would like to have the convenience of using a credit card for their purchases. Compare cards with no international transaction fees from our partners below.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '2022', '', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:05:37', '2016-03-29 01:35:34', '4827a704-cfd7-4032-bbab-eb5eaa0ffe56'),
 ('102', '113', 'en_us', 'Hotel Credit Cards', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Are you looking for a hotel card? From the budget-minded to the luxury traveler, the right credit card can enhance your travel experience. The following hotel cards from our partners offer a variety of benefits at some of your favorite hotels including complimentary stays, membership status, and room upgrades. If convenience is top priority when you travel, and you aren\'t loyal to one hotel chain, check out some of the flexible rewards cards listed below instead. Flexible rewards cards allow you to redeem points for hotel travel expenses, regardless of the hotel brand.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '2314', '', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:06:01', '2016-03-29 01:37:29', '92a50043-77fe-450b-9973-ea8c0784ab22'),
 ('103', '114', 'en_us', 'Travel and Airline Credit Cards', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The following travel credit cards from our partners offer airline or hotel rewards. You can earn frequent flyer miles or rewards points when you travel or when you spend. The frequent flyer miles or rewards points can be redeemed for airline discounts or free nights at participating hotels. If you are a frequent flyer or travel a lot, an airline or travel credit card could help save you money.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '16', '3181640', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:06:06', '2016-03-31 01:17:42', '84ad539b-4894-4f59-be6a-6414945caac9'),
 ('104', '115', 'en_us', 'Reward Credit Cards', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The following reward credit cards from our partners feature either cash back or rewards programs. Rewards Program Credit Cards \"reward\" you for using them with cash back incentives and rebate programs.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '14', '3181642', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:06:26', '2016-03-29 01:40:05', '175566e2-2d80-4c76-828b-712994e90536'),
 ('105', '116', 'en_us', 'Points Rewards Credit Cards', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The following Points Reward credit cards from our partners feature the ability to earn reward points for card purchases. Reward points can then be redeemed for a variety of items, including merchandise, gift cards or cash back. Apply today for the Points Reward credit card of your choice by completing a secure online application.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '77', '3497323', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:06:33', '2016-03-29 01:43:10', '4d6b93bf-5daf-4b2d-86fb-f96697932673'),
 ('106', '117', 'en_us', 'Gas Cards', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The following Gas Rebate credit cards from our partners allow consumers to earn higher cash back rebates for gas purchases along with 1% on all other purchases. With Gas Rebate credit cards you can reduce the high cost of driving with your everyday credit card spending. Apply for the gas card of your choice today by completing a secure online application. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '79', '', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:06:38', '2016-03-29 01:44:35', 'd676e80b-f1da-4670-bddc-edf625e337fc'),
 ('107', '118', 'en_us', 'Good Credit', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The following Credit Cards are for People with Good Credit. Compare offers side by side and apply online for the card that is right for you. Apply for the Good Credit credit card of your choice by completing a secure online application.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '75', '', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:07:01', '2016-04-02 15:32:08', 'c5f98a3a-b73e-4e88-83e0-1fc1602186af'),
 ('108', '119', 'en_us', 'Fair Credit', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The following Credit Cards and Prepaid Debit Cards are for People with Fair Credit. Compare offers side by side and apply online for the card that is right for you. Apply for the Fair Credit credit card or prepaid debit card of your choice by completing a secure online application.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '74', '', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:07:07', '2016-04-02 15:29:43', '55371a5c-1b46-4e17-aafe-3eb15bb494eb'),
 ('109', '120', 'en_us', 'Bad Credit', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Simply getting a credit card will not help you build or re-establish your credit history. Making on-time minimum payments with all of your creditors and keeping account balances low relative to the credit limit are key to building your credit history. Prepaid debit cards, unlike credit cards, do not provide a line of credit and do not influence your credit history. Choose from secured and unsecured credit cards, and prepaid card offers below - some of them are fee-based.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '20', '', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:07:12', '2016-04-02 15:32:46', '1e718d5d-f839-4c8f-996b-ca596307a6b8'),
 ('110', '121', 'en_us', '﻿﻿Limited or No Credit History', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p class=\"category-description\">The following Credit Cards and Prepaid Debit Cards are for people with   limited or no credit history. Compare offers side by side and apply   online for the card that is right for you. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<a href=\"/credit-card-news/credit-card-law-interactive-1282.php\">Federal laws impose restrictions on issuing credit cards to individuals   under 21 unless the applicant has the independent ability to repay debt   or has a co-signer over the age of 21 who agrees to accept joint   liability for the account. </a></p>\r\n\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '1077', '', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:07:40', '2016-04-02 15:31:13', '60047bff-5c1e-4598-8116-83be4a03e3aa'),
 ('111', '122', 'en_us', 'Debit Cards & Prepaid Cards', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The following Debit cards and Prepaid cards from our partners can help you control your spending. If you tend to overspend or would like to control your spending then a debit card or a prepaid card could be a good card for you. Debit cards & prepaid cards are not credit cards.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '19', '', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:08:06', '2016-04-02 15:20:03', '4d5d8f16-ea23-4bb3-beb5-ec859a61f816'),
 ('112', '123', 'en_us', 'Secured Credit Card Options and Offers', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Secured credit cards are a tool that can help you establish or build your credit history. Unlike prepaid cards, secured credit cards provide you with access to a credit line, and your payment activity will be reported to the major credit bureaus. Only you can build a good credit history. Make your payments on time each month, and keep your balance low relative to the credit limit, for positive marks on your credit report. Please note: before any secured card can be activated, it MUST be funded with a security deposit equal to the credit line.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '1768', '', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:08:20', '2016-04-02 15:22:24', '7aeb3cf4-7c75-4c49-8b2d-55af75146023'),
 ('114', '125', 'en_us', 'Business Credit Cards', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>A small business credit card or corporate credit card can help you keep your company\'s expenses on track and obtain the buying power you need to operate your business. Some business credit cards also reward you for all your business purchases in the form of cash back or airline miles. Learn more in these <a href=\"http://www.creditcards.com/credit-card-news/credit-cards-for-small-business-owners-stories.php#Credit_cards_for_small_business_owners\" target=\"_blank\">articles and tips on credit cards for small business</a>. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Compare the business credit card offers from our partners below and apply for the card that\'s right for you. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '17', '3181641', NULL, '2016-03-24 13:08:44', '2016-04-02 15:38:34', '46e0d0d6-5515-4f7d-ae35-127128bfe144'),
