 ('219', '271', 'en_us', 'Personal Loans', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Are you looking for credit card alternatives? We’ve compiled a list of emergency loans and peer-to-peer lending options to help you with your search. Emergency loan options can help deal with short-term financial emergencies, while peer-to-peer lending options can give borrowers access to funds for a variety of purposes, often at lower interest rates than traditional credit cards.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '2372', '', '<p>Emergency personal loans are not right for everyone. Learn about how these loans work before you consider applying for one. This type of short-term loan can help you deal with a financial emergency. Typically, the loan amount, along with interest, will need to be paid in full with your next paycheck. The interest rate and fees may be very high, making this an expensive way to borrow money. Additionally, this type of loan may not help you build a stronger credit score. </p>', '2016-04-02 18:10:10', '2016-04-02 18:13:30', '1142b956-8f9c-45a0-9538-0ebe87a1b1aa'),
 ('220', '272', 'en_us', 'Small Business Loans', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Whether you are looking to purchase equipment and inventory for your business, refinance existing business debt, or expand to a new location, a small business loan could be right for you. Small business loans and lines of credit can be smart alternatives to business credit cards, often offering lower interest rates than their credit card counterparts. Compare business credit options from our partners below to find the best financing option for your business.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '2345', '', 'Small Business Loans are not right for everyone. Learn about how these loans work before you consider applying for one. This type of short-term loan can help you deal with a financial emergency. Typically, the loan amount, along with interest, will need to be paid in full with your next paycheck. The interest rate and fees may be very high, making this an expensive way to borrow money. Additionally, this type of loan may not help you build a stronger credit score.							', '2016-04-02 18:15:34', '2016-04-02 18:15:34', '7a83062b-978d-4854-b638-3d1e8b99b519'),
 ('221', '273', 'en_us', 'Limited Time Offers', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The credit card offers below are available for a limited time only. Some of these cards reward you in the form of cash back or points. Hurry, these offers from our partners may not last long.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'standard', '2018', '', '<p>See the online credit card specials applications for details about terms and conditions of offer. Reasonable efforts are made to maintain accurate information. However all credit card information is presented without warranty. When you click on the \" Apply Now \" button you can review the credit card terms and conditions on the credit card issuer\'s web site.</p>', '2016-04-02 22:44:34', '2016-04-02 22:44:34', '7f5b7004-0b2b-4c8b-a492-9aefa104170d'),
